            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile treatment gallery: 79% of searches on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Lunch break treatment search = phone. Non-responsive gallery = they find another spa. Mobile-optimized photos = they book. Beauty treatments = mobile impulse bookings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-fuchsia-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Practitioner credentials visible: 53% more trust</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Our injectors: RN-certified, 10+ years experience" prominently. Month 1: 53% more qualified bookings. Credentials = safe = skilled = choose you.</p>
            </div>
